Quote: Cammock employs chemical topping to create specific high quality clover-dominant pastures for weaner calves and finishing lambs. Another farmer to try chemical topping is Pahiatua's Bill Wallace, who has been experimenting with the method for the last three years to suppress grasses and weeds on selected areas with shady faces and Californian thistle.
